    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Gameplay:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sudden Market is a <strong>very fast paced first person action game</strong> that takes place after the closing of a supermarket. Each level has a shopping list, complete it <strong>within the time limit without getting caught by the security guards</strong>. First, find the products, then collect them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special products will appear on the ground. Pick them up to <strong>dash, escape guards, or push them out of your way</strong>. Once you’ve collected everything, head to the checkout gates and <strong>pay before time runs out</strong>.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217560/extras/f4068d174aace47520315e4c3ea9bfd7.poster.avif?t=1756028188\" aria-label=\"Gameplay GIF\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217560/extras/f4068d174aace47520315e4c3ea9bfd7.webm?t=1756028188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217560/extras/f4068d174aace47520315e4c3ea9bfd7.mp4?t=1756028188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Levels:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are <strong>18 levels across 2 maps</strong>. You can easily <strong>keep track of your best time with the time comparison</strong> displayed at the end of each level. Your time is converted into a score, which can be viewed in the main menu. <strong>Replay levels to improve your best score</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The early levels are simple</strong>, but the <strong>later ones become much more challenging.</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217560/extras/a720c2fd095424d155b3d701fc466dfc.avif?t=1756028188\" alt=\"Illustration image\" width=616 height=218 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Additional informations:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some levels include extra obstacles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Other shopping carts move around the supermarket. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Security guards have 3 difficulty levels: easy, intermediate, and hard.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are multiple security guards in the final levels. </p></li></ul>",
